{"page":1,"results":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2580822,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Luigi Antonini","original_name":"Luigi Antonini","popularity":0.1294,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/5meDobtdG4t0d45NK3SoM5u17Ve.jpg","id":16322,"name":"X Factor","original_name":"X Factor","overview":"X Factor is the Italian version of the British musical talent show The X Factor. The first four seasons aired on Rai 2, but since 2011 it has been broadcast on Sky Uno, with reruns on TV8, after Rai dropped the show due to high costs. Sky Italia acquired the format, extending its broadcast until 2024. Starting from the eleventh season, RTL 102.5 became the official radio station, replacing Radio Deejay and Radio 105. The show was hosted by Francesco Facchinetti (2008-2010), Alessandro Cattelan (2011-2020), Ludovico Tersigni (2021), and Francesca Michielin (2022-2023). From 2024 onwards, Giorgia will take over as host. Since the seventh season, the show has been produced by Fremantle Italia without the collaboration of Magnolia, which had produced the selection episodes in the early seasons.","poster_path":"/tGIDuv3ySOGk8agG34fKMZI7BTB.jpg","media_type":"tv","original_language":"it","genre_ids":[10764,10751],"popularity":8.4741,"first_air_date":"2008-03-10","softcore":false,"vote_average":7.5,"vote_count":11,"origin_country":["IT"]},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/8UwHGS3KnkZgRXCvgYTCVA7leST.jpg","id":1351959,"title":"Annalisa - Tutti in Arena","original_title":"Annalisa - Tutti in Arena","overview":"The program featured Annalisa performing songs from her discography.  During the show, the singer-songwriter also duetted on songs by five musical guests: “Eppure sentire (un senso di te)” with Elisa, “La genesi del tuo colore” with Irama, “Superclassico” with Ernia, ‘Tango’ with Tananai, and “Come saprei” with Giorgia.","poster_path":"/g0Uz7qqOXWs352MYT0qxJVxbkjt.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"it","genre_ids":[10402,10770,99],"popularity":0.0589,"release_date":"2024-09-05","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.0,"vote_count":2},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/dfzqkB6bcP9UxLLVsd8Y6rd8lQX.jpg","id":889639,"title":"Claudio Baglioni - In questa storia che è la mia","original_title":"Claudio Baglioni - In questa storia che è la mia","overview":"A total opera-concert based on songs from the album In questa storia che è la mia (In this story that is mine), recorded in 2021 at the Teatro dell'Opera with words and music by Claudio Baglioni, under the artistic direction of Giuliano Peparini, television direction by Luigi Antonini, and featuring the artistic ensembles of the Teatro dell'Opera.","poster_path":"/yJVE7ZNNQMyKew6GTKPHxd0yWsv.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"it","genre_ids":[10402],"popularity":0.0916,"release_date":"2021-11-02","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":10.0,"vote_count":1}]}],"total_pages":1,"total_results":1}